name: GOSU Development
short_description:
Provide and promote Design and Development ideas, tools and source code for all users/projects using GOSU. The purpose of this open source project is to enable personnel and projects using GOSU to jump start projects with a sound and stable foundation in development and ensure delivery of robust solutions.


NOTE: To successfully compile and run code you will need either the open source GOSU Development platform or products based off GOSU (including the Guidewire Insurance Platform®©) 

NOTE: The Guidewire Insurance Platform and all references to it are used solely for identification purposes only and is/are all the property of, and solely owned by, Guidewire Software Inc.
